node.title: Missing Auckland man found dead near Manukau Heads
node.description: The body of missing Weymouth man Nick Paul has been located at Orua Bay near Manukau Heads, police say.
node.content:
["The body of missing Weymouth man Nick Paul has been located at Orua Bay near Manukau Heads, police say.", "", "
Manukau Heads at entrance from Tasman Sea into Huia Bay. File image. Photo: 123RF
", "In a statement, Police said they were notified after a body was located on the beach at Orua Bay over the weekend.", "Police subsequently identified the body as 46-year-old missing Weymouth man Nick Paul.", "The death will be referred to the coroner."]
